physical_appearance: This is a photograph of a river in Rangoon, Burma. The foreground of the photograph is a riverbank. There is a boat in the middle of the river. In the background, there are some buildings along the other side of the riverbank. The title is printed at the bottom, below the photograph.
title_text: Photograph album of views and portraits in the Punjab, Cashmere, Ceylon, Burma, Penang, Singapore, and Java River in Rangoon
